1.4.name: wordpress/wiki-embed
1.4.description:
The Wiki Embed's intent is to help create a (http://wiki.ubc.ca/Resource_Management_Framework "Resourse Management Framework").

This plugin will pull content from any Media Wiki website (Such as wikipedia.org). It strips and reformats the content, allowing you to supply some arguments to dictate how this works.
